{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "# Entity 功能模块总览\n\n小说 TXT → 章节解析 → 实体预扫 → LLM 抽取 → 校验/消歧 → 入库 → 人工审核/导出",
      "x": -760,
      "y": -520,
      "width": 760,
      "height": 180
    },
    {
      "id": "web",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## web 前端\n\n- UploadPage：上传 TXT、启动提取\n- LibraryPage：书库列表\n- ReviewPage：人工审核角色/地点/物品\n- DashboardPage：看板\n- SettingsPage：LLM 配置",
      "x": -1120,
      "y": -220,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 250
    },
    {
      "id": "api",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## api 后端\n\nFastify 服务\n\n- /books：上传、列表、内容、删除\n- /books/:id/extract：启动/状态/SSE进度\n- /characters、/locations、/items：实体审核更新\n- /export/:bookId：导出\n- /health/llm：LLM 状态与配置",
      "x": -620,
      "y": -220,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 300
    },
    {
      "id": "storage",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## storage 数据层\n\nPrisma + SQLite\n\n核心表：\n- User\n- Book\n- Character\n- Location\n- Item\n- CharacterReview\n- ExtractionSession\n- Task",
      "x": -620,
      "y": 180,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 280
    },
    {
      "id": "scheduler",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## scheduler 调度层\n\nTaskDispatcher + Queue\n\n阶段顺序：\n1. extractor\n2. validator\n3. entity-resolution\n4. reviewer\n\n职责：创建任务、重试、事件通知、阶段完成后传递 payload、最终更新 Book 状态。",
      "x": -80,
      "y": -220,
      "width": 430,
      "height": 320
    },
    {
      "id": "import",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## import 增强导入\n\nparseTxtEnhanced\n\n1. preprocess：文本归一化/去噪\n2. splitChaptersStructured：章节切分与结构化\n3. prescanEntities：实体预扫",
      "x": 460,
      "y": -520,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 260
    },
    {
      "id": "prescan",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## entity-prescan 实体预扫\n\n对象：人物、地点、物品、事件\n\n流程：\n- 正则扫描\n- 全文角色发现\n- 可选 LLM 补全\n- 别名规范化\n- 置信度过滤\n- 重要度评分\n- 分层输出 core/supporting/candidate/archive",
      "x": 980,
      "y": -520,
      "width": 460,
      "height": 330
    },
    {
      "id": "extractor_stage",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Stage 1: Extractor\n\n输入：Book.filePath\n\n处理：\n- 读取小说文本\n- 调用 parseTxtEnhanced\n- LLM 按 30 章/批抽取角色/地点/物品\n- 角色与预扫结果融合\n- 过滤 0 提及 + 0 对白的幻觉角色\n- 地点/物品用预扫补充提及数、章节覆盖、重要度\n- 调用 story-arcs 生成故事资产",
      "x": 460,
      "y": -120,
      "width": 520,
      "height": 390
    },
    {
      "id": "llm_prompts",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## llm + prompts\n\nLLM provider 抽象：\n- ollama\n- custom\n- mock\n\nprompts：\n- 角色/实体抽取\n- 校验\n- 实体消歧\n- 故事弧线",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": -80,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 260
    },
    {
      "id": "story_arcs",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## story-arcs 故事资产\n\n从章节和预扫结果构建：\n- story segments\n- narrative events\n- characters in story\n- scenes\n- props\n- episode plan\n- storyboard/video prompt pack",
      "x": 1040,
      "y": 260,
      "width": 400,
      "height": 260
    },
    {
      "id": "validator",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Stage 2: Validator\n\nvalidators 模块\n\n职责：\n- validateCharacters\n- validateEntityBatch\n- 低置信度过滤\n- 缺字段检查\n- 非法名称检查\n- 实体去重/别名冲突检查",
      "x": 460,
      "y": 380,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 280
    },
    {
      "id": "resolution",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Stage 3: Entity Resolution\n\nentity-resolution 模块\n\n职责：\n- 同名合并\n- 中文姓名归一\n- 安全别名匹配\n- 规范名选择\n- 清洗泛称/集体称谓\n\n输出：合并后的角色列表 + merged 数量",
      "x": 980,
      "y": 620,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 300
    },
    {
      "id": "persist",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Dispatcher 入库\n\n在进入 Reviewer 前持久化：\n\n- Character\n- Location\n- Item\n\n默认 status = PENDING\n\n地点/物品保存重要度字段：importanceScore、tier、storyScore、productionScore、pillar*、mentionCount、chapterAppearances。",
      "x": 460,
      "y": 780,
      "width": 470,
      "height": 310
    },
    {
      "id": "reviewer",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## Stage 4: Reviewer\n\n当前逻辑：\n- 实体已经写入 DB\n- 标记为等待人工审核\n- 返回 Characters ready for human review\n\n随后：\n- 写 pipeline final summary\n- Book.status = EXTRACTED\n- eventBus 发 completed",
      "x": -80,
      "y": 780,
      "width": 430,
      "height": 300
    },
    {
      "id": "review_ui",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 人工审核 UI\n\nReviewPage\n\n功能：\n- 角色/地点/物品 Tab\n- PENDING / APPROVED / REJECTED 过滤\n- 单个通过/拒绝/编辑\n- 批量通过/拒绝\n- 查看原文内容",
      "x": -620,
      "y": 640,
      "width": 420,
      "height": 280
    },
    {
      "id": "exporters",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## exporters 导出\n\n支持格式：\n- JSON\n- Markdown\n- CSV\n\n当前 API 主要导出 characters。",
      "x": -1120,
      "y": 640,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 220
    },
    {
      "id": "scripts",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 脚本入口\n\n- run_producer.mjs：走 Producer/调度管线\n- run-extract.ts：直接读文本、调用 LLM 抽取、写 output/entities\n- test_full_pipeline.mjs：管线验证脚本",
      "x": -1120,
      "y": 160,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 230
    },
    {
      "id": "output",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "## 文件输出\n\n- .intermediate/{run}/prescan：预扫中间文件\n- output/{book-run}/：最终摘要和故事资产\n- output/{book-run}/entities：characters/items/locations/summary",
      "x": -80,
      "y": 360,
      "width": 430,
      "height": 230
    }
  ],
